        <mj-text font-weight="600">
          <p>Your 5-point e-commerce supply chain management formula</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          <p class="fs-italic">“Given that the barrier to switching brands is low in the retail and fast-moving consumer goods (FMCG) industries, the longer each shelf is left empty, the more business is lost to the competition. However, ensuring seamless restocking across multiple locations is often an uphill battle. Efficient shelf replenishment requires overcoming complex logistics challenges through strategic solutions.”</p>
