        <mj-divider padding-top="20px" padding-bottom="20px" border-width="0.5px" border-color="#290A38" />
        <mj-text font-weight="600">
          <p>Why omnichannel retail is the future of shopping in the Middle East</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          <p class="fs-italic">“Optimizing order management, route planning and delivery slot management are some of the key focus areas to improve efficiency, keep costs in check and offer superior customer experiences at the last mile. Cutting-edge logistics solutions leverage advanced algorithms that optimize routes and delivery schedules, accommodating over hundreds of constraints to achieve these goals.”</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-weight="600">
          <p class="fs-italic">- Nishith Rastogi, CEO & Founder of Locus</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-weight="600">
